{"tid":2121840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：不排除關閉更多中國使領館","createTime":"2020-07-23T14:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T15:29:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"662ddbdde04a9872e0547aeb9ac2195877c4be43","tid":2121840,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:43:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539518-20200723.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539518-20200723.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=a3d44a06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539518-20200723.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4acd0524\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539518-20200723.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國政府要求中國駐休斯敦總領事館，在72小時內，即當地星期五下午4時前關閉，中國駐休斯敦總領事蔡偉接受傳媒訪問時表示，知道這個消息後感到十分震驚，批評美方的舉動沒有底線、蠻橫無理。<br />\n<br />\n對於外界指總領事館焚燒文件，蔡偉稱各國外交機構遇到緊急情況，都會採取一些措施，這個是慣例，沒有甚麼大驚小怪，批評美國傳媒炒作。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，不排除會關閉更多中國的使領館。"},{"pid":"7ca9b24fb7e4451d6f70b9c9f0c0b58caf2d62be","tid":2121840,"uid":212702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"改為台灣註美領事館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a907b6f71bd89231827bbb68518086cb828299","tid":2121840,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe9815a4524c5d3d4ca95205c9a06b32ad91a87","tid":2121840,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n